I wasn't going to do a video tonight; I was going to take the day off, but I felt in my spirit we could just talk over some things real quick and we'll pray.

00:02:01.440 --> 00:02:12.119
We saw a lot of progress in our prayers for the nations even from the last 48 hours when we did those back-to-back videos.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:24.319
I told you I believe with all my heart God has assembled the greatest prayer group of any generation for such a time as this with people like you.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:39.359
He said, "Braden, I'm bringing my best,"and I truly believe it, that the veterans and the newbies, the ones that are learning how to pray, I'm telling you, I really believe we're changing things.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:45.466
And so, finding these weapons of mass destruction has been on my heart all day.

00:02:45.467 --> 00:02:55.119
I truly believe they're in the northeast, underneath this mountain. I keep seeing this mountain.

00:02:55.120 --> 00:03:01.719
And if you go back to what we were looking at yesterday, I'll give a little recap real quick.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:13.701
I saw the man with the black hat hiding. I don't know; it sounds like they found him today. I don't know if this is true.

00:03:13.702 --> 00:03:26.475
I'm getting a lot of fake news, so you don't know who is real and who is not, but some people say that he was injured and they took his leg.

00:03:26.476 --> 00:03:35.806
Benny Johnson on his show tonight was saying that they believe that he was injured and they might have taken his leg off because of the injuries that he's sustained.

00:03:35.807 --> 00:03:47.439
I don't know if that's fake news or not, but as I continue to pray, I believe that the Lord is going to deal with this man, too.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:54.073
Some people say he's worse than the last one. There's so much news.

00:03:54.074 --> 00:04:03.919
There's so much stuff coming in that I said, "What do you believe and what do you not believe?"You have to really just filter it and go with what you're praying over.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:19.704
President Trump declaring that he believes the war is over; the economy, like I told you—Israel hit, from what I understand, every oil and gas plant in Iran.

00:04:19.705 --> 00:04:32.999
And if that is true, if they've hit every single one of them, this is exactly what the Lord showed us in our prayer time back in June of last year.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:59.754
And he told us that Israel would strike all the oil wells and the oil refineries, and there would be war on the Strait of Hormuz. We see that happening.

00:04:59.755 --> 00:05:19.832
Oil went up to $120 a barrel today as crude was skyrocketing because of the news of Israel, and then Iran hit one of Israel's main oil plants and their gas plants where they make diesel and everything else.

00:05:19.833 --> 00:05:24.439
They hit their largest plant, from what I understood last night.

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:38.298
So, they struck their oil wells; they blew up all of theirs. When that happened, oil shot up to $120 a barrel. Now, President Trump came on and said, "The war is over.

00:05:38.299 --> 00:06:07.714
It looks like we're about over."Then oil started going back down when he and Putin said they were coming to an agreement on lifting the sanctions off of the oil for trade with Russia, which I know President Trump probably is trying to help our economy and he doesn't want people mad at him because midterms are coming.

00:06:07.715 --> 00:06:23.199
If you have gas lines and $10-a-gallon gas, you're going to have a lot of upset Americans.

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:45.738
As we're praying into these things and seeing it, I believe the visions that the Lord shows me are so prayer changes things—that we don't have the gas lines, that we don't have massive gas prices go above $10 a gallon, and the anti-Semitism and all the things that the Lord has shown me.

00:06:45.739 --> 00:07:00.559
I know because part of the vision has already come true. The war with Iran, the striking of all the oil wells—that part of the vision has happened, manifested completely.

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:07.639
The gas lines and oil going to $200 a barrel—this is the part where it split.

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:21.965
And so far it only went to $120. No gas lines. It's interesting to me, the things that I see and we're praying over.

00:07:21.966 --> 00:07:32.382
Between all channels, we had probably 150,000 people pray over that last night.

00:07:32.383 --> 00:07:40.039
I'm not quite to 200,000, but just a little under with all seven channels.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:46.852
I give all the glory to God. There's so many of you that come out and pray like that.

00:07:46.853 --> 00:07:51.902
I know the power of prayer. If you get one of us to pray, good; two agreeing touching anything...

00:07:51.903 --> 00:08:02.879
just think about almost 200,000 people praying for up to two or three hours.

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:18.371
That's amazing. I believe that we're changing things. I pray we don't see gas go up to $10 a gallon.

00:08:18.372 --> 00:08:24.641
That would be terrible and it would affect our economy greatly.

00:08:24.642 --> 00:08:30.374
Half of it is in the news, half of it's not. The power of prayer there.

00:08:30.375 --> 00:08:39.399
Number two, the Lord showed us yesterday, I believe, one weapon.

00:08:39.400 --> 00:08:53.312
And as I was in the spirit again, I could hear that new leader talking to a scientist. "Does it work?"I could hear him in English.

00:08:53.312 --> 00:09:40.399
"Does it work?"The scientist, in a white outfit, said, "It has not been tested yet, but we believe we have successfully built the bomb."It was ready to put on a rocket; it looked as long as a school bus, like a massive city bus.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:47.935
That's how big this thing was—a fat, round-looking rocket.

00:09:47.936 --> 00:09:52.805
They were pointing at this rocket saying that could be the payload.

00:09:52.806 --> 00:10:01.602
They were discussing this one thing. They only had one, but it was not tested.

00:10:01.603 --> 00:10:12.959
They said, "So, we don't know if it will work, but we all believe that it will.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:20.759
We only have one."And I believe that was a nuclear something.

