If you go back to what the Lord said: Hiroshima. Go back to that. That was an atom bomb.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:46.439
It wasn't like what we have now, these great big ones, but it was still something very significant that hit Japan in World War II.

00:10:46.440 --> 00:11:01.680
The Lord told us this, but as I was hearing this scientist talking to the man with the black hat, black turban, they kept talking back and forth: "What do we have at our disposal?

00:11:01.681 --> 00:11:21.679
What bigger artillery do we have underground?"They were discussing things, getting ready for a surprise attack against Israel with biological weapons.

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:28.479
I saw biological weapons. I saw containers that were underneath the ground.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:42.359
They were separated out by Agent Orange. And there were three different kind of things.

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:51.599
