00:11:51.600 --> 00:12:03.528
It was in a black drum, but in the spirit I could see a color on it. The next one was red.

00:12:03.529 --> 00:12:18.479
They only had about six or seven barrels stacked up three high.

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:33.796
The others were over here and I could see them being stored, but there was a lot of it—50 or 60 barrels or more.

00:12:33.797 --> 00:12:54.653
This one looked red, and I saw on it the letter Y. I'm still praying about it, but it was some kind of biological weapon, chemical warfare.

00:12:54.654 --> 00:12:57.971
It was right next to it. That was something in the spirit realm.

00:12:57.972 --> 00:13:05.719
When I was looking at it, there was something that looked like another kind of object, but I couldn't focus on it.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:10.838
The visions come very fast and whenever I'm looking, so many things are coming at me.

00:13:10.839 --> 00:13:21.046
I don't take the time, because I'm on a live stream, to pause it and try to look into it. That's the trouble with being live.

00:13:21.047 --> 00:13:46.639
If it were in my private time, I would spend all day on that because I pray over it, and what I've learned to do is freeze-frame it in the spirit and just pray specifically over those biological weapons for hours and be able to focus in and look around them.

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:57.399
It is all by the Spirit of God, all to the glory of God. I didn't do that last night, though I wish I would have now.

00:13:57.400 --> 00:14:09.025
I saw the missiles. They were painted black. Some were big, some were small.

00:14:09.026 --> 00:14:23.279
I believe with all my heart this is under a mountain in the northeast area of Iran, closer to Afghanistan.

00:14:23.280 --> 00:14:39.195
Turkmenistan is northeast up here, and this is Afghanistan.

00:14:39.196 --> 00:14:46.879
