00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:25.133
It wasn't commercial; it wasn't used in a Ford F-150. It was used in spacecraft. I thought that was interesting.

00:18:25.134 --> 00:18:42.200
I saw secret weapons that we are about to use that will make the earth shock in awe at the technological advancements we have achieved only by the hand of God.

00:18:42.201 --> 00:18:51.403
The Lord said, 'I have restrained it where China has not been able to touch this.'I have held this back so that China...

00:18:51.404 --> 00:18:58.782
you know, it's like you have a block. You're able to see certain things because you're using part of your brain you never knew you had.

00:18:58.783 --> 00:19:07.827
